43
00:03:34,940 --> 00:03:35,910
Give me your phone.

44
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:38,850
Please, don't bother
and worry about yourself.

45
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:40,650
Why are you going in?
I have to head out.

46
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:45,460
My goodness, look at this mess.

47
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:47,590
Jeez.

48
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:50,630
