with this acting stuff.

49
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,730
Unbelievable.

50
00:03:57,070 --> 00:03:59,100
Are you still on sleeping pills?

51
00:03:59,100 --> 00:03:59,970
Wait.

52
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:02,740
These are just vitamins. I stopped.

53
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:03,870
Like hell you stopped.

54
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,640
You think I'm a fool?

55
00:04:06,180 --> 00:04:07,410
Good grief.

56
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:10,910
I was out of my mind to let you
drop out of a perfectly good college...

57
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:14,780
