your daughter perform, even once?

65
00:04:34,570 --> 00:04:36,870
You threw away that bright future
ahead of you...

66
00:04:36,870 --> 00:04:38,070
and now live like this.
That's why I'm telling you this.

67
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,680
Bright future? Don't make me laugh.

68
00:04:41,710 --> 00:04:43,680
