and I've got nothing left.

78
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,410
I'll pay you
when the money comes in later.

79
00:05:43,410 --> 00:05:45,140
I got fooled again.

80
00:05:55,620 --> 00:05:57,690
Then I can't just hand it over to you
for free.

81
00:05:59,220 --> 00:06:03,090
(Phone repair, used phones)

82
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:04,590
What kind of phone do you want?

83
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:06,200
- Anything's fine.
- Anything?

84
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,730
All right then.

85
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:08,570
Excuse me.

86
00:06:11,470 --> 00:06:12,740
I left it there. Just take it.

87
00:06:16,410 --> 00:06:17,440
Ta-da.

88
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,610
It's a prepaid plan, okay?

89
00:06:20,710 --> 00:06:22,450
Look, let me explain.

90
00:06:22,910 --> 00:06:25,480
Here's prepaid 350,

91
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,320
and prepaid 450.
If you use it on H or G network...

92
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:30,290
A criminal ring
running a voice phishing scam...

93
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:33,220
